/apps/2594540/extras/4c00cc969d8ce1438302aaf13cad6d71.mp4?t=1752541428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>you can add a lot of ideas to your motel, such as payphones and vending machines to make more money. Or build a bus station to attract more customers. You can even place ads in your motel area to generate more cash (if you have the required popularity).<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Renovate, clean, furnish and expand an abandoned motel.<br></li><li> Design your rooms and equip them and make them ready to accept guests.<br></li><li> Order shipments, fill shelves with different products.<br></li><li> Hire employees to help you in your journey.<br></li><li> Manage your stock, prices and upgrade your work places.<br></li><li> Serve customers and keep them satisfied.</li></ul>",
